" The keywords of each group were defined as follows:
spastic* (spastic, spasticity), muscle tone, muscular tone, hyperton* (hypertonia, hypertonic, hypertonicity);
assess* (assess, assessment), measure* (measure, measurement), quanti* (quantify, quantification, quantitative);
technolog* (technology, technological), instrument* (instrument, instrumental, instrumented), mechatronic, mechanical, muscle activity measurement, electromyography, EMG, sEMG, inertial measurement unit, IMU, force sensor, dynamometer, ergometer, robot* (robot, robotic, robotics), kinematic* (kinematic, kinematics, kinematical)."
